						<summary>

						<p>Hero-stone near the Hanumān temple.</p>						

						<p>12th century A.D.</p>						

						<p>This fragmentary and worn out inscription is not clear. Seems to state that Īśvara was holding the office of <hi rend="italic">gāmuṇḍu.</hi></p>						

						<p>The characters belong to about 12th century A.D.</p>						

						</summary>
